      "You can achieve some parts of the `tsvector` functionality by using multi indexes and `split`. For example:\r\n```\r\ntable.indexCreate(\"text\", function(x) { return x('text').split(\" \"); }, {multi: true})\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever that doesn't take care of removing words like \"a\" or converting plural into singular nouns."
